tabla_mas_baja <- letra %>% 
  mutate(fecha = year(fecha)) %>% 
  filter(fecha == 2022) %>% 
  group_by(fecha,letra_desc) %>% 
  summarise(w_mean = round(mean(w_mean),0)) %>% 
  arrange(desc(w_mean))
`summarise()` has grouped output by 'fecha'. You can override using the `.groups` argument.
